<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>But God chose the foolish things of the world to shame the wise; God chose the weak things of the world to shame the strong.  He chose the lowly things of this world and the despised things - and the things that are not - to nullify the things that are, so that no one may boast before him.</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
